        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I've read through code for `ex_restart` in [ex_docmd.c](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/a69f2db773b85e03c631a5eb3a37f43098288194/src/nvim/ex_docmd.c#L4990) but I still don't understand the restart lifecycle well enough to add to `:h startup`.\r\n\r\nWould it be between steps 4 and 5 in [`starting.txt`](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/a69f2db773b85e03c631a5eb3a37f43098288194/runtime/doc/starting.txt#L443)?",
