        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I would need some more time to be able to prove it via the tests, but is the current approach not early enough?\r\n\r\nUsing this init.lua it is available at all of the logged times:\r\n```lua\r\n_G.log = {}\r\nlocal log_variable = function(state) table.insert(_G.log, { state, vim.v.startreason }) end\r\n\r\nlog_variable('init.lua')\r\nvim.api.nvim_create_autocmd('VimEnter', { callback = function() log_variable('VimEnter') end })\r\nvim.api.nvim_create_autocmd('UIEnter', { callback = function() log_variable('UIEnter') end })\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/user-attachments/assets/9c80c35e-3a55-4d84-81c3-185e768630a1\r\n\r\n\r\n",
            "created_at": "2026-06-16T06:18:52Z",
